Further information
A multinational firm are expanding their presence in South East Asia, and they have recognised great potential in Indonesia. Their business plan for Indonesia started last year and it has now reached a stage where they can expand their team locally.
They are seeking high calibre actuaries or actuarial students of the Indonesian Actuarial society to join their growing team and service their multinational clients on the ground. They look to train you up to be a Qualified Actuary so you can progress into crucial positions in the company and sign off documents for the business. Advanced Prophet modelling skills are highly desirable.
Overseas Indonesians looking to return to the country are welcome. EA Licence Number: 13S6608
